          <note type="general">See Thiruvengadathan pg. 17 and Raghavan introduction to Śāhendravilāsa pg. 41</note>
          <note type="general">Written at the instance of Nīlakaṇṭha Dīkṣita (see Raghavan, introduction to Śāhendravilāsa pg. 41)</note>
          <note type="general">Here, Rāma's omnipotence is described and his arrows are eulogised, in Sragdharā metre (see Sinhā pg. 306–307)</note>
